title: Resident Lounge and Game Room, The Summit Lounge, Washer and Dryer
posting_body: ['521 Stadium Place S, Seattle, WA 98104', 'The Wave takes modern design to new heights.', 'This 26 story apartment tower has an unparalleled look, location and breathtaking views (from up here you can see the 12th Person!).', 'The Wave is part of Stadium Place, a modern community designed so you can live, work and play in Seattle’s most famous neighborhoods.', 'The Wave luxury apartment homes offer floor to ceiling windows, top end finishes, quartz counters, air conditioning, walk in closets and wood flooring along with two roof top lounges with stunning views, a massive courtyard, high tech theater and a spa like fitness center.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Mobile Kitchen Island', 'Air Conditioning', 'High-End Finishes', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Washer and Dryer', 'Stainless-Steel Appliances', 'Community Features:', 'Onsite Controlled Access Parking and Storage', 'Business and Conference Center', 'Resident Package Lockers', 'Fitness Center and Yoga Room', 'Pet-Friendly Community with Two Dog Runs and a Paw Spa', 'Private Courtyard', 'Resident Lounge and Game Room', 'The Summit Lounge', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and Availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Contact us today for the most up to date information.']
